#!/bin/bash
tput init 
 end = $ (($ (tput colors) - 1)) 
 w = 1 
 for c
  in $ (seq 0 $end) 
  do
eval "$(printf " tput setaf % 3 s " " $c ")" 
      echo - n "$_" 
      [[$c - ge $ ((w * 2))]] 
      offset = 2 || offset = 0 
      [[$ (((c + offset) % (w - offset))) - eq $ (((w - offset) - 1))]] 
      echo 
 done 
 tput init
